.title
VICAR Program spot2vicar - logs SPOT image file to VICAR
.help
PURPOSE

     SPOT2VICAR logs SPOT image and metadata. This includes
     creating an RPC and storing in VICAR file.

.PAGE
TAE COMMAND LINE FORMAT

     spot2vicar inp outpre
     
     where

     inp         is a SPOT DIMAP input image
     band        is a zero-based band selecting a band from the particular image

     options
       band  selects one of several bands in a multispectral image; 
             zero-based index
       sl, ss, nl, ns specify a subarea to log
       rpc   "y" to calculate and put rpc in VICAR output file

.PAGE
OPERATION

.PAGE

